Requirements:

	Android(> 2.2,froyo)

Installation:

	1:Download the alipi.apk file from this link https://github.com/rakendu-droid/Alipi-Android-tool/downloads

	2:Change the setting in the phone to allow installation from "unknown sources"(settings->applications->unknown sources)
	
	3:Click on the alipi.apk in the sd card and follow the instructions to install the application.

	4:Start the application and enter a url which has re-narration(a11y.in/a11y_fs/). 
	
	5:After the web-page loads,press the menu button and choose "renarrations". 

	6:After choosing the language and author, The web-page loads with the re-narrated content